messages.message: Hi. Is it possible to start a chat project in a shared workspace? i see some chat projects sitting in some of the shared workspaces. But when i try to create one in a shared workspace it says that i can only create it on my workspace. Also the Ai Hub docs says i can create a char project in a shared workspace. screenshots of both below!
@BG We don't support creating chat in the shared workspaces. @avi also brought up the same and we are looking into this.
